extendedInfo.description: Join the Society of Critical Care Medicine for the 42nd Critical Care Congress in San Juan, Puerto Rico. The 2013 Congress curriculum is packed with world-renowned speakers, interactive workshops, thought-provoking panel discussions, stimulating educational sessions, and the opportunity to earn continuing education credits. Download this app to manage your schedule and gain access to full program details. Keywords: SCCM, Critical Care Congress, 2013, SCCM Congress, 42nd Congress, SCCM 2013
